# proxy.list — extra generic-foreign domains (supplements remote lists)
# Target group: Proxy
# Format: one rule per line, TYPE,value  (NO trailing policy).
#
# Most generic foreign routing is handled by remote rule-sets in the template
# (YouTube, Netflix, Twitter, Telegram, etc.) plus FINAL -> Proxy. Add domains
# here for foreign sites you want on Proxy that upstream lists miss.
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,wikipedia.org
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,medium.com
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,v2ex.com
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,reddit.com
